desc_short	-----								TIKI GALORE is an online multiplayer arena where Players are Tiki Warriors armed with deadly spears and an even deadlier thirst for domination. Players battle enemy Tikis on a tropical island with an active volcano and ancient temples surrounded by Tiki-eating shark-infested waters.							
